{"tid":1522180,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大火=防禦工事，起好就要走","createTime":"2019-08-31T12:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:51:06.000Z","uid":64981,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c71953cdb1d6767de73f1a1fcfe634ef870eb0","tid":1522180,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:28:28.000Z","msg":"火唔會幫你攻得入狗總，只可以令防暴狗無法推進同拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n所以，當大火已經起好，大家應該做嘅係反方向慢慢撤退，搵下一站繼續打。<br />\n<br />\n今日見到有人起完火之後，企喺原地唔肯走，等火救熄之後，俾速龍一次過拉曬。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好撚心痛。<br />\n喺呢個位置俾人拉，係一定坐勁多碌。</span>"},{"pid":"a835e2a8691f2ea61254ceccf98a09cc42dc4e3c","tid":1522180,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885bff5af2ea41d87234666d797620ced00c45c9","tid":1522180,"uid":64981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:29:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2149e60049122d01b87db51bfc9517b5830e1681","tid":1522180,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接用梘</span></span></strong><br />\n有手足試過work呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sKMOCQq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKMOCQq.jpg&h=02d62fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外國當年purple Rain Protest水炮車顏料示威者<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">都係用番梘</span></span></strong>洗=洗得甩<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yz5jKvV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYz5jKvV.jpg&h=1413a946&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻煩大家幫手spread開去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPush"},{"pid":"550afc73bbe1a43d521c19470d5d75